OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FThe CCA puts the UK Government in
OL,8,Fcharge of decision-making, with
OL,9,Fdevolved administrations left to
OL,10,Fimplement them.
OL,12,FHowever, because Covid-19 was not
OL,13,Fconsidered an "unforeseen event" the
OL,14,FCCA could not be used.
OL,16,FInstead, public health powers were
OL,17,Fdrawn on, meaning the devolved
OL,18,Fgovernments, including in Wales,
OL,19,Foversaw their own responses.
